@client\src\components\HomePage\freedomWall\FreedomWallPage.jsx 6. Visual Aesthetic
Right now, Iskrib has a very clean, "Modern Web" look. The Freedom Wall should look different to signal a "playful" zone.

Improvement: Use a different background texture (like concrete, a corkboard, or a dark "chalkboard" style) specifically for that page. This visually tells the user: "The rules are different here."

